      "value": "<p>Your creature companion can unleash its fury unbidden.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites: Creature Companion Master, Survival 13 ranks.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit: </strong>Each round on your turn, after you act and only if you didn&rsquo;t grant your creature companion any actions, your creature companion can forgo its normal move action to make a full attack with a &ndash;4 penalty to its attacks. You can control your creature companion at a range of 120 feet.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
